data.description: This ranch-style home is situated in the Chubbuck area and features a total of five bedrooms and two bathrooms. Three of the bedrooms are located on the main level, while the remaining bedroom and bathroom are in the basement. The main level also comprises a dining area, living room, and family room. The house has a spacious fenced backyard, and it is conveniently located near Stuart Park, Splash Pad, and Chubbuck Library. The seller is offering a $5,000 allowance, so call today to get more details.
